{"type":"message","id":"f24c1058","parentId":"a0a920f1","timestamp":"2026-06-30T01:00:00.218Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Tuesday, June 30th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-30 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1782781200215}}
{"type":"message","id":"c029a42a","parentId":"f24c1058","timestamp":"2026-06-30T01:02:05.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that fires daily to remind me of Cursor collaboration rules. The user wants me to silently confirm. Let me just acknowledge this is noted and don't send any message back - it's a system reminder."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n📋 Cursor 协作规则已确认记住。\n\n1. 任务提交：`submit_task.py --title --instructions --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify`\n2. 确认回复：`confirm_write.py --task-id --decision auto --reply`\n3. 查看队列：`submit_task.py --list`\n4. 查看结果：`submit_task.py --results`\n\n静默确认，无需回复。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782781200217}}
